---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About Us" description="Learn about the Scandinavian Hard Dance Alliance - our vision, mission, and the values that drive us.">
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>About SHDA</h1>
      <p class="lead">United by passion, driven by hard dance music</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-section">
        <h2>Our Vision</h2>
        <p>
          <!-- TODO: Update with real vision statement -->
          The Scandinavian Hard Dance Alliance (SHDA) envisions a thriving, interconnected hard dance
          community across the Nordic countries. We believe in the power of music to unite people
          and create unforgettable experiences. Our vision is to become the leading network for
          hard dance organizers in Scandinavia, setting the standard for collaboration, quality,
          and passion in event organization.
        </p>
        <p>
          We strive to create a sustainable ecosystem where organizers, artists, and fans can
          connect, grow, and celebrate the music we all love. Through unity and cooperation,
          we aim to elevate the hard dance scene to new heights across Sweden, Denmark, Norway,
          and Finland.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-section">
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>
          <!-- TODO: Update with real mission statement -->
          Our mission is to support and empower hard dance event organizers who are driven by
          genuine passion for the music, not just profit. We achieve this through:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Quarterly networking meetings bringing together organizers from all Nordic countries</li>
          <li>Collaborative event planning and cross-promotion opportunities</li>
          <li>Shared resources for bookings, pricing, and infrastructure</li>
          <li>Joint marketing initiatives and social media strategies</li>
          <li>Knowledge sharing about artists, venues, and best practices</li>
          <li>Coordinated transport solutions and event takeovers</li>
          <li>Mentorship for emerging organizers and companies</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="content-section">
        <h2>Our Story</h2>
        <p>
          <!-- TODO: Update with real history -->
          Founded in 2024, the Scandinavian Hard Dance Alliance emerged from a shared recognition
          among leading organizers across the Nordic countries: we are stronger together. What began
          as informal conversations between Forced 2 Dance and fellow organizers quickly evolved
          into a formalized network dedicated to mutual support and growth.
        </p>
        <p>
          Starting with a core group of passionate founders, SHDA has grown to include some of
          the most respected names in Scandinavian hard dance. From event organizers to travel
          companies, our members share a common goal: to create exceptional experiences for
          hard dance fans while supporting each other's success.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-section">
        <h2>Our Values</h2>
        <div class="values-grid">
          <div class="value-card">
            <h3>Passion Over Profit</h3>
            <p>
              We organize events because we love the music. While sustainability is important,
              our primary drive is creating amazing experiences for our community.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="value-card">
            <h3>Collaboration</h3>
            <p>
              We believe in working together, sharing knowledge, and supporting each other.
              Competition is healthy, but cooperation makes us all stronger.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="value-card">
            <h3>Quality</h3>
            <p>
              We are committed to high standards in every aspect of event organization,
              from artist bookings to venue selection to fan experience.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="value-card">
            <h3>Inclusivity</h3>
            <p>
              Hard dance is for everyone. We welcome all who share our passion, regardless
              of background, and work to create safe, inclusive spaces.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="value-card">
            <h3>Sustainability</h3>
            <p>
              We build for the long term, ensuring our events and organization practices
              are environmentally and financially sustainable.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="value-card">
            <h3>Innovation</h3>
            <p>
              We embrace new ideas, technologies, and approaches to continuously improve
              and evolve the hard dance scene.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="content-section">
        <h2>What We Do</h2>
        <p>
          SHDA operates as a collaborative network with several key activities:
        </p>
        <div class="activities-list">
          <div class="activity">
            <h4>Quarterly Meetings</h4>
            <p>
              Four times a year, members gather to share insights, plan collaborations,
              and strengthen our network. These meetings rotate between countries to
              ensure accessibility for all members.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="activity">
            <h4>Event Collaborations</h4>
            <p>
              We organize joint events, artist bookings, and cross-promotional campaigns
              that benefit all members and expand the reach of hard dance across Scandinavia.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="activity">
            <h4>Resource Sharing</h4>
            <p>
              From equipment and infrastructure to marketing materials and industry contacts,
              we pool resources to reduce costs and improve quality for everyone.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="activity">
            <h4>Knowledge Exchange</h4>
            <p>
              Members share expertise on everything from pricing strategies to social media
              marketing, helping each other grow and improve.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="content-section cta-box">
        <h2>Join Us</h2>
        <p>
          Are you a hard dance organizer or company in Scandinavia who shares our values?
          We're always looking to connect with passionate individuals and organizations
          who want to contribute to our growing community.
        </p>
        <a href={`/contact`} class="btn btn-primary">Get in Touch</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    padding: var(--spacing-4xl) 0 var(--spacing-2xl);
    text-align: center;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--color-bg-primary) 0%, var(--color-bg-secondary) 100%);
  }

  .page-hero h1 {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .page-hero .lead {
    color: var(--color-accent-cyan);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }

  .content-section {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-4xl);
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .content-section h2 {
    color: var(--color-accent-cyan);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  .content-section p,
  .content-section ul {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
  }

  .content-section ul {
    margin-left: var(--spacing-xl);
  }

  .content-section li {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .values-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--spacing-xl);
    margin-top: var(--spacing-2xl);
  }

  .value-card {
    background-color: var(--color-bg-secondary);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.2);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: var(--spacing-xl);
    transition: all var(--transition-base);
  }

  .value-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-accent-cyan);
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.2);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .value-card h3 {
    color: var(--color-accent-cyan);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .value-card p {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .activities-list {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--spacing-xl);
    margin-top: var(--spacing-xl);
  }

  .activity {
    background-color: var(--color-bg-secondary);
    padding: var(--spacing-xl);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent-cyan);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
  }

  .activity h4 {
    color: var(--color-text-white);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .activity p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }

  .cta-box {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.1) 0%, rgba(157, 0, 255, 0.1) 100%);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-accent-cyan);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: var(--spacing-2xl);
    text-align: center;
    max-width: none;
  }

  .cta-box h2 {
    color: var(--color-text-white);
  }

  .cta-box p {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .page-hero h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    .values-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
